ChargeOptions.description: Specifies charge options for NSF and Notices in PascalCase. Possible values names are: NSFDefault, NSFRemainPosted, PostedNonNSFDisregarded, NSFPaid, NonPostedNSFReturned, PostedNSFReturned, NonPostedNSFPaid, OneNotice, PrintCurrentBalance, SeparateNotices, NoNoticeForChargeBacks. ExemptNSFFees, ExemptNegativeBalanceFees, ExemptExcessDebitFees.
